snippet.title: Preserve | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Preserve is a relaxing puzzle nature-building game in which you flourish a vibrant ecosystem by cleverly placing plants and animals to create a perfect symbiosis to your liking.

WISHLIST Preserve now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2109270/Preserve/
Follow Preserve on Social Media: https://linktr.ee/preservegame
Check out Preserve website: https://www.preserve-game.com/
